|WKBCharisma:                    Range: |YKB1-200

    |YKOCharisma is a measure of force of personality. It measures how well a
character is able to influence others by word or action. A charismatic
character is more likely to be listened to, respected, and trusted by
others. If you have a high charisma, the shopkeepers might give you some
extra gold just because they like you. Charisma is useful for guilds that
require some subtlety in their dealings, or who seek to guide people
along a particular path.
